    "body": "Hey @Haroenv ,\r\n\r\nThank you so much for your super quick and helpfull response.\r\nYes I see the guide on customisation on the site but I don't get it. \r\nConcerning the data, I need the hits and the facet results. For example, if I do my search on the films. I will need the values of 'category' and 'year' attributes and their stats to show the distribution of films by category or year ..\r\n\r\nThe connectors seems to be a good solution, I will try it and tell you the results..\r\n\r\nThank you again for your help ..",
