    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Aha, for having the data on the facets, you can use [connectMenu](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors/connectMenu.html) or [connectRefinementList](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors/connectRefinementList.html)\r\n\r\nI'll close this for now, but feel free to reopen if there's more information needed. \r\n\r\nIt would also be helpful afterwards if you posted your stats solution (it's very innovative 🎉) on our [forum](https://discourse.algolia.com/c/show-tell)",
